➜眼睛黑矇、晕眩是中风前兆？颈动脉狭窄要当心！
https://pansci.asia/archives/197537	3600
<ul><li>作者／崔源生医师</li><li>本文转载自 Care Online 照护线上《<a href="https://www.careonline.com.tw/2020/10/carotid-stenosis.html">眼睛黑矇、晕眩，中风前兆要当心，颈动脉狭窄懒人包</a>》，欢迎喜欢这篇文章的朋友订阅支持<a href="https://www.careonline.com.tw/"> Care Online </a>喔</li></ul>
<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img loading="lazy" width="560" height="293" src="http://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/98378a53a07bf39cda14480750672114-560x293.png" alt="" class="wp-image-197542" srcset="https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/98378a53a07bf39cda14480750672114-560x293.png 560w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/98378a53a07bf39cda14480750672114-510x267.png 510w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/98378a53a07bf39cda14480750672114-273x143.png 273w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/98378a53a07bf39cda14480750672114-350x183.png 350w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/98378a53a07bf39cda14480750672114.png 740w" sizes="(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px" /></figure></div>
<p>「老伴，你怎麼啦？」老太太与老先生说着话，突然老先生用手撑着头，反应有点异常。</p>
<p>「刚刚眼前黑矇一片，头晕晕的。最近偶尔会这样。可能只是用眼过度，或是最近比较疲劳吧！」老先生回过神回答。</p>
<p>「会不会是中风前兆啊？赶快去医院检查看看！」老太太警觉地说。</p><div class="pansc-content"></script>
<!-- leaderboard -->
<ins class="adsbygoogle"
